  <amendments/>
  <summary>9/10/1998--Introduced.
Energy Efficient Technology Tax Act - Establishes: (1) an energy credit based on the energy efficiency of energy properties and passenger vehicles; (2) a reforestation credit; and (3) a credit for certain nonbusiness energy property. Defines terms. Increases the exclusion allowed from gross income as a "qualified transportation fringe" benefit. Extends, by five years, the placed in service date of a qualified energy resources facility.</summary>
</bill>
